jeremyText="This waits on the ceiling until you're under it, then comes crashing down after you. The speed they come down after you is dependent on the difference in your y coordinates. They can also dive toward you along x depending on various circumstances." chaoText="These were in all the Metroid games except Fusion, though they are in that game's code. In Metroid Prime, they were named 'Shriekbats'." devText="In the original game, these have an animation while they wait on the ceiling. For this, I wanted them completely still to hide them more from the player."
